description: Braided-net fringe, Pieced, striped lining. Black wool ground with polychrome silk embroidery. There is a wide woven silk edging with silk and cotton tassels. The backing is woven striped cotton. Two tassels near bottom corners are inset bound above woven edge. Lower left corner has 2 tassels underneath.
